@startuml
!theme plain
title Policy Guru Chatbot - Deployment and Connectivity Flow

actor User
participant "Chainlit UI\n(app.py)" as Chainlit
participant "Agent\n(agent_utils.py)" as Agent
participant "Langchain\nTools" as Tools
participant "Qdrant\nVector DB" as Qdrant
participant "OpenAI API" as OpenAI
participant "Google Search\nAPI" as GoogleSearch
participant "Data Preloader\n(main.py)" as Preloader
participant "S3 Bucket" as S3
database "Shared Volume\n(/dataset)" as Volume

== System Initialization & Data Preloading ==

Preloader -> S3: Download Policy PDFs
activate Preloader
activate S3
S3 --> Preloader: PDF Documents
deactivate S3

Preloader -> Preloader: Split PDFs into chunks\n(document_utils.py)
Preloader -> OpenAI: Generate embeddings
activate OpenAI
OpenAI --> Preloader: Embeddings
deactivate OpenAI

Preloader -> Qdrant: Load embeddings and chunks
activate Qdrant
Qdrant --> Preloader: Confirmation
deactivate Qdrant

Preloader -> Volume: Store dataset
deactivate Preloader

== Chatbot Runtime - User Interaction ==

User -> Chainlit: Ask question about policy
activate Chainlit

Chainlit -> Agent: Process question
activate Agent

Agent -> Agent: Determine appropriate tool\n(Chain of Responsibility)

alt Policy Search Tool
    Agent -> Tools: Invoke Policy Search
    activate Tools
    Tools -> Qdrant: Query with embeddings
    activate Qdrant
    Qdrant --> Tools: Relevant policy chunks
    deactivate Qdrant
    Tools -> OpenAI: Generate answer with context
    activate OpenAI
    OpenAI --> Tools: Response
    deactivate OpenAI
    Tools --> Agent: Policy answer
    deactivate Tools

else Web Search Tool
    Agent -> Tools: Invoke Web Search
    activate Tools
    Tools -> GoogleSearch: Search insurance news
    activate GoogleSearch
    GoogleSearch --> Tools: Search results
    deactivate GoogleSearch
    Tools -> OpenAI: Format results
    activate OpenAI
    OpenAI --> Tools: Formatted response
    deactivate OpenAI
    Tools --> Agent: Web search answer
    deactivate Tools

else Greeting Tool
    Agent -> Tools: Invoke Greeting
    activate Tools
    Tools --> Agent: Greeting response
    deactivate Tools
end

Agent --> Chainlit: Final answer
deactivate Agent

Chainlit --> User: Display response
deactivate Chainlit

== Feedback Collection ==

User -> Chainlit: Provide feedback (positive/negative)
activate Chainlit
Chainlit -> Qdrant: Save feedback
activate Qdrant
Qdrant --> Chainlit: Confirmation
deactivate Qdrant
Chainlit --> User: Feedback recorded
deactivate Chainlit

== Health Check ==

Preloader -> Preloader: Health check endpoint
note right: Periodic monitoring

@enduml
